emember my friend Jake, but I would like to bring him  with me.<br> <b>B:</b> Jake would be welcome. If you think of anyone else, feel free to bring them  along also.<br> <b>A:</b> What would you like me to bring?<br> <b>B:</b> Everything is taken care of, but if you and Jake want to bring something to  drink, that would be appreciated.<br>
